                            %p Thank you for your thoughtful nomination of #{@nominee.full_name}.  The application made by #{@nominee.full_name} has been received and will now be vetted by UEI.  Notification of partner status will be made by early January 2012.
                            %p Thank you again for your efforts to help grow the 100Kin10 movement.
                            %br/
                            %p
                              Thanks,
                              %br
                              The 100Kin10 Team
                  %tr
                    %td{:align => "left", :bgcolor => "#ffc427", :valign => "top"}
                      %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "20", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "100%"}
                        %tr
                          %td{:align => "left", :style => "font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#FFFFFF;", :valign => "top"}
